    "feat": {
        "name": "Advanced First Aid",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "You use your medical training to ameliorate sickness or assuage fears. When you use Medicine to Administer First Aid, instead of Stabilizing a character or Stopping Bleeding, you can reduce an ally\u2019s frightened or sickened condition by 2, or remove either of those conditions entirely on a critical success. You can remove only one condition at a time. The DC for the Medicine check is usually the DC of the effect that caused the condition.",
        "level": 7,
